      "value": "<p>You tap into your inner feline power, moving at incredible speed, nearly impossible to track.</p><ul><li>You can teleport up to your remaining movement speed up to a place you can see (This consumes the amount of movement speed you teleport).</li><li>You can then attempt to Hide as a free action.</li><li>On a successful Stealth check, if you are not in the open or in bright light, you become hidden.</li></ul>",
